{"tid":1358540,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［對準政權］7.27 反送中 反警黑勾結 反黑勢力治港","createTime":"2019-07-24T02:59:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T04:35:55.000Z","uid":55257,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"85112e1c72b378c49ec8b6f4bee4f9512f68c9ae","tid":1358540,"uid":55257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T02:59:46.000Z","msg":"7.27大遊行強烈建議認清目標，主調應該是反送中、抗惡法；反官警黑勾結、反黑勢力治港，訴求一定要清晰！<br />\n<br />\n基於各自爬山的精神，我唔會反對燒村拆祠堂，但係請大家三思，小心憤慨淹沒了理智，我地抗爭的對象係港共政府、黑警、黑社會以及係背後包辦一切的中共。<br />\n<br />\n雖然呢幾日大量事件發生，當中不少大快人心，但係我地必需冷靜落黎，沈澱一下，回想整個抗爭運動的初心：<br />\n<br />\n重申對特區政府的五大訴求：<br />\n<br />\n一、撤回逃犯條例修訂<br />\n二、收回612暴動定性<br />\n三、撤銷所有反送中抗爭者控罪<br />\n四、成立獨立調查委員會追究警隊濫權、官警黑勾結<br />\n五、立即實行真正的雙普選<br />\n<br />\n我們熱愛香港，不願再有香港人為守護家園而流血，甚至犠牲寶貴性命。<br />\n<br />\n但我們強調&mdash;&mdash;「沒有暴民，只有暴政」，我們誓必以一切方法迫使政府完全正面回應並實現我們的訴求。<br />\n<br />\n我們促請政府盡快回心轉意，使香港重回正軌，成為團結、民主、自由、公義的社會。<br />\n<br />\n7.27<br />\n元朗見"},{"pid":"d5bb31d4f717296760441b0432c91cffcc4b63ff","tid":1358540,"uid":165246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T03:00:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請大家一定要記得！！！！<br />\n１。全面撤回逃犯條例<br />\n２。撤銷暴動定性<br />\n３。釋放被捕義士並承諾永不追究<br />\n４。全面實行雙普選<br />\n５。成立獨立調查委員會追究黑警責任＋徹查警黑勾結元朗站暴打站內市民<br />\n6 。721上環對示威者開36槍 義士被狗開槍擊中 下落不明<br />\n要求公佈義士下落<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"f58f8448421e78f91525125bf4f348d9ccc0f75b","tid":1358540,"uid":55257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T03:09:13.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"45377266edfedcc44ea3c2924aa023aff6a45f9d","tid":1358540,"uid":55257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T03:13:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"592100907f566a2dd8981120c28e1d3d017de97a","tid":1358540,"uid":55257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T03:26:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"66c74d93f6ea8d45613f510f396813b7f31b7a09","tid":1358540,"uid":151248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T03:53:11.000Z","msg":"星期三啦<br />\n抖夠好推返正經post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"158db864f385f2bc4bbcee4a3c5a45bf976619f7","tid":1358540,"uid":55257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T04:30:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f7ac8b825b32b8abc90765fc131cdf80433248b1","tid":1358540,"uid":134778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T04:31:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"93ae1e5f6fb65d16b1619d275f5a4a99b0fedea8","tid":1358540,"uid":55257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T04:31:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"617ea40442bea1792c701729af5363f930d8596b","tid":1358540,"uid":237077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T04:31:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5aNwFaC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5aNwFaC.jpg&h=d84b994a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"41de2b6a970fa4842e0dd853ad7702eb66605b33","tid":1358540,"uid":55257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T04:35:55.000Z","msg":"推"}]}